      "description": "An absolute benchmark of mechanical integrity. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated power plant paired with a tactile six-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original rigidity, supported by an active damping system and precision-aligned suspension geometry. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors with zero thermal degradation. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, including a clean borescope and fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on forged alloys. This is an investment-grade, turn-key example for the discerning driver.",
